Thanks for checking out the Pardot API!

common.xsd
opportunities.xsd
Describe the responses given by the Pardot API. For more information about XSDs, check out the Wikipedia article: http://goo.gl/ECFav

pardot-wadl.xml
This WADL file describes Pardot's API methods, which are documented at http://developer.pardot.com. The WADL is used to configure an Apigee API console, which can be used at http://help.pardot.com/api. Please contact us at help at pardot.com if you have any questions or issues.
